  "description": "<p><strong>Introductions:</strong><br/>Do you fall in love with this Glarry GST Stylish Tiger Stripe Electric Guitar Kit with Black Pickguard the first sight you see it? We offer this electric guitar for its perfect performance, stylish appearance as well as its reasonable price. Designed with a black pickguard, this guitar looks more charming and unique than others. With humanized design and high quality, it is durable to use. What is more, the standard tone from this guitar gives you wonderful audio experience. Featuring comfortable hand feeling and melodious tone quality, this electric guitar will be your regretless choice!</p>\n <p><strong>Features:</strong><br/>1. H-H Pickup get a deeper, louder and smoother sound compared to cheaper single coil<br/>2. With White pickguard on the surface, this guitar looks cool and could be well protected<br/>3. Comfortable hand feeling, stylish outlook, stable performance and melodious sound<br/>4. A perfect solution for beginners who want to learn to play guitar<br/>5. An addicting instrument that can be taken everywhere<br/>6. This electric guitar throws in incredible value to quickly become a guitar that grabs your attention<br/>7. It has a silky balance to the tone that supports vocals beautifully<br/>8. Best choice for yourself or as a gift for your dear friends<br/>9. It comes with speaker, guitar bag, shoulder strap, plectrum, crank, connecting wire and spanner tool etc<br/>10. 1/4 inch headphone output jack, used for silent practice<br/>11. 1/8 inch auxiliary input jack, used for MP3 player</p>\n <p><strong>Specifications:</strong><br/>1. Style: Electric Guitar<br/>2. Brand: Glarry<br/>3. Body:<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Orientation: Right Handed<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Body: Basswood<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Color: Blue<br/><br/>4. Neck and Fingerboard<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Neck: Maple<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Fingerboard: Rosewood<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Strings: 6<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Frets: 24<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Nut width: 1.656 in. (42 mm)<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Scale Length: 25.5\"<br/><br/>5. Pickups &amp; Hardware:<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Pickups: Humbucker-Humbucker Pickup<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Control: 3 Way Switch; 1 x Volume; 2 x Tone<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Hardware: Tremolo<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Jack: 1/4\"<br/><br/>6. 20W Electric Guitar Amp<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Front Panel Controls: Gain\uff0cBass\uff0cTreble, Volume, Headphone<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Bass Guitar Input: (1/4\" Jack)<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Headphone output: (1/4\" Jack, Speaker defeating)<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Dimensions: 29*27*11.3cm<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Weight: 3.0 kg<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Speaker Size: 8.5 inch<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Impedance: 4\u03a9<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Auxiliary input jack (MP3): 1/8 inch<br/><br/>7. Dimensions<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Guitar Dimensions: (39.17 x 12.99 x 2.36)\" / (100 x 33 x 6)cm (L x W x H)<br/>\u2022&nbsp; Gutiar Weight: 6.3kg / 13.89lbs</p>\n <p><strong>Package Includes:</strong><br/>1 x Electric Guitar<br/>1 x 20W Electric Guitar AMP<br/>1 x Electric Guitar Bag<br/>1 x Guitar Strap<br/>1 x Tremolo Arm<br/>1 x Amp Wire<br/>1 x Wrench Tool<br/>1 x Amp Wire<br/>1 x Wrench Tool</p>\n <p>Warm Note\uff1aWARNING USE OF SPEAKERS: TO REDUCE THE RISK OF FIRE OR ELECTRIC SHOCK DO NOT EXPOSE TO RAIN OR MOISTURE INDOOR USE ONLY, AND PLEASEl UNPLUG THE SOCKET IMMEDIATELY WHEN THE SPEAKER IS NOT IN USE. RISK OF ELECTRIC SHOCK DO NOT OPEN<br/></p>\n <p><br/></p>\n <p><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/ab2d9e5a-9082-47cb-9f8b-521b4a3afd01.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/b40e3cc0-6f4c-4a92-8fdb-6ba418d62b46.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/a08d20b2-656a-4a8e-8c15-685a54e7a74a.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/59d2e43e-781e-44fc-ae29-a2d52e726f1f.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;\" contenteditable=\"false\"/><img src=\"https://cf.cjdropshipping.com/847cbd71-f9bb-46c0-80f9-1781eb9dd6